      "content": "hey i been struggling with sleep so bad lately. i take melatonin every night but it doesnt really do much anymore. my doctor gave me some zolpidem to help but i dont wanna take it yet since i might need it later. do u think its okay if i just take the melatonin and the zolpidem together tonight to see if it works better? i really need to catch up on sleep.",
