      "content": "i get that a doctor is better but i cant wait for an appointment next week. i'm just so exhausted. i read online that they don't actually interact badly since they work on different pathways in the brain, so one just helps the other out. wouldnt it be fine just to do it once to see if it helps me get through tomorrow? it's not like i'm taking a ton of it.",
